OL,3,CBotched BBLs: Glasgow bans company and
OL,4,Cpractitioner after woman hospitalised
OL,6,FTwo companies and an aesthetics
OL,7,Fpractitioner have been banned from
OL,8,Fcarrying out Brazilian Butt Lifts in
OL,9,FGlasgow after a woman was taken to
OL,10,Fhospital following a BBL procedure.
OL,12,FITV News understands the companies
OL,13,Finvolved are Lift Aesthetics, London
OL,14,FBBL Limited and the practitioner is
OL,15,FRicky Sawyer.
OL,17,FITV News has been investigating them
OL,18,Fall for more than six months.
