OL,6,FEnforcement action was taken by the
OL,7,Fcouncil after a following a BBL
OL,8,Fprocedure in a hotel function room in
OL,9,FMarch this year.
OL,11,FThe health and safety prohibition
OL,12,Fnotices prohibit those involved from
OL,13,Fundertaking any BBL or breast
OL,14,Faugmentation procedures within any
OL,15,Fpremises or locations within the
OL,16,FGlasgow City Council local authority
OL,17,Farea until evidence can be provided
OL,18,Fthat these procedures will be carried
OL,19,Fout safely.
